 "Reduce an image over multiple geometries at once. ",
 Cell["featureCollection", "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->
  "80ccda8d-0ae7-2a41-a141-62094c8b98eb"],
 " is a GEE FeatureCollection expression, ",
 Cell["reducer", "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->
  "a7070da3-0a38-3e49-a164-defbb243776b"],
 " is a reducer name (e.g., ",
 Cell["\"mean\"", "InlineCode",ExpressionUUID->
